OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781046185
OL,3,CThree pupils injured after stabbing at
OL,4,Ca school
OL,6,FOfficers from Greater Manchester
OL,7,FPolice say they're currently
OL,8,Fresponding to an incident at a school
OL,9,Fon Plant Hill Road, Blackley where a
OL,10,Fschoolgirl has been arrested.
OL,12,FCo-op Academy is reportedly on
OL,13,F'lockdown' and pictures from the scene
OL,14,Fshow a huge emergency services
OL,15,Fpresence, with police and ambulance
OL,16,Fvehicles pictured outside the school
OL,17,Fgates and inside the school grounds.
OL,19,FA helicopter is also reportedly flying
OL,20,Foverhead.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
