OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781046185
OL,3,CThree pupils injured after stabbing at
OL,4,Ca school
OL,6,FGMP has released a statement, saying a
OL,7,Fschoolgirl has been arrested and three
OL,8,Fpeople, who aren't further described,
OL,9,Fhave been injured.
OL,11,FIt's understood the three people
OL,12,Finjured suffered injuries consistent
OL,13,Fwith a knife.
OL,15,FIn the statement, police said the
OL,16,Finjuries, thankfully, 'aren't believed
OL,17,Fto be serious at this time'.
OL,19,FGMP said: "Emergency services remain
OL,20,Fon scene and we are supporting the
OL,21,Fschool.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
